Package org.neo4j.kernel.diagnostics

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DiagnosticsReporterProgress
    Interface for handling feedback to the user.
    DiagnosticsReportSource
    A diagnostic source is a pair of a destination and a function to create input stream of data to be written to that destination.
    ProgressAwareInputStream.OnProgressListener
    Interface for classes that want to monitor this input stream
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DiagnosticsOfflineReportProvider
    Base class for a provider of offline reports.
    DiagnosticsReporter  
    DiagnosticsReportSources
    Contains helper methods to create create DiagnosticsReportSource.
    DiagnosticsReportSources.DiagnosticsFileReportSource  
    DiagnosticsReportSources.DiagnosticsStringReportSource  
    InteractiveProgress
    Tracks progress in an interactive way, relies on the fact that the PrintStream echoes to a terminal that can interpret the carrier return to reset the current line.
    KernelDiagnosticsOfflineReportProvider  
    NonInteractiveProgress  
    ProgressAwareInputStream
    Implements an InputStream that keeps track of the progress.
